    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for by a single owner. It looks and drives exactly as it did when it first left the dealership, with a flawless exterior finish and an interior that still smells new. Every feature works perfectly, and the mechanical components have been maintained to the highest standard, ensuring a smooth and powerful driving experience. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that is indistinguishable from a brand-new model.",
