      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of distinguished character and proven reliability. This unit has been maintained to a rigorous standard, ensuring both mechanical integrity and a refined driving experience. An excellent opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a balance of performance and value. Thoroughly inspected and prepared for immediate acquisition.",
