    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has plenty of life left in it for its next owner! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is totally ready to go. I've taken great care of it, and it still runs like a dream. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin or have any questions at all\u2014I'm super happy to help!",
      "price": 29500.0,
